Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.06,0:24:06.05,Tonari-Sign-top,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Opens Summer 2013?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.70,0:24:10.24,Tonari-main,Oshi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's from Yuu-chan.
